data.description: Ready to enjoy the salt life? This all brick 3 bedroom 2 bath home is located approximately 6 miles from the Hang Out and Gulf Shores public beach. It has a spacious open concept that’s great for entertaining family and friends. The kitchen has ss appliances, pantry and granite counter tops. The living area has a fireplace and French doors accessing the screened in back patio and fenced back yard. The primary bedroom has 2 walk-in closets, jetted tub and a seperate shower. The location is convenient for shopping and entertainment. New metal roof 2019. 2 year old Washer and dryer. Short term rentals are a minimal of 60 days. Call and schedule your private showing today.
